The People of the State of New York, Respondent, v. Thomas Caruso, Appellant.

Order, entered on October 8, 1965, unanimously affirmed. No opinion. The order of this court, entered on March 22, 1966 [25 A D 2d 720], is vacated.

Concur — Breitel, J. P., Rabin, McNally, Stevens, and Eager, JJ.
